              "text": "## Additional reading on issue trees:\n* Check out this link to a blog that walks through the 8 steps of [McKinsey's Problem solving framework](https://medium.com/@IliyanaStareva/8-step-framework-to-problem-solving-from-mckinsey-506823257b48)\n* [McKinsey Problem Solving Methodology](https://collaborate.uchicago.edu/depts/bcs/TestSite/Clone_Consulting/Consulting%20Resources/General_McKinsey%20Problem%20Solving%20Method.pdf)",
