              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "## Exercise 1: Issue Tree \n\nYou are Data Science Manager for Nordstrom and have a meeting with your manager on how you plan to prioritize and structure your team’s work for the next 2 weeks. Use the problem statement provided to develop an issue tree.\n\n__ Example problem statement:__\n\nWhy has customer retention in the past 3 months declined when compared to others?\n\n*For simplicity, customer retention can be defined as the definite churn of a customer 60 days after his or her initial purchase.\n\n\n\n\n",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            }
          ]
