            {
              "id": 848171,
              "key": "5d8a44a6-e198-480f-a769-a2349e365be9",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "## Issue Tree Exercise: Solution\n__Example problem statement: __\n\n__Why has customer retention in the past 3 months declined when compared to others?__\n\n1. Have customers stopped buying the product?<br>\na. Have they graduated out of buying the product?<br>\nb. Did they opt out because of price?<br>\nc. Did they opt out because of quality?<br>\nd. Was the product not a necessity?<br>\ne. Is the frequency of purchase greater than 30 days?<br>\n2. Have customers switched to alternatives?<br>\na. Have they began to buy competitor products that are higher quality?<br>\nb. Have they began to buy competitor products that are cheaper?<br>\n\n\n\n",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            }
          ]
